graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>Kubeflow Component]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|required<br/>platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22.0+<br/>CRD & workload orchestration]
    NotebookController -->|required<br/>framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.15.0<br/>Operator framework]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|optional<br/>metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]
    NotebookController -.->|optional<br/>ingress routing| Istio[Istio<br/>VirtualService creation]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|code import| CommonHelpers[kubeflow/components/common<br/>Go module - shared utilities]
    NotebookController -->|runtime| JupyterImages[Jupyter Notebook Images<br/>Container images]
    NotebookController -.->|ingress gateway<br/>if USE_ISTIO=true| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>External access]

    %% Integration Points - ODH Components
    JupyterHub[JupyterHub<br/>Multi-user notebook launcher] -->|creates CRs| NotebookController
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI] -->|creates/deletes CRs| NotebookController

    %% Integration Points - Kubernetes Components
    K8s -->|watch events| NotebookController
    NotebookController -->|creates resources| StatefulSets[StatefulSets<br/>Notebook pods]
    NotebookController -->|creates resources| Services[Services<br/>ClusterIP routing]
    NotebookController -->|creates resources| VirtualServices[VirtualServices<br/>Istio routing]

    %% External Services
    NotebookController -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    StatefulSets -->|image pull| Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]

    %% Observability
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes| NotebookController
    K8s -->|health probes| NotebookController

    %% Styling
    style NotebookController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Internal ODH dependencies
    style CommonHelpers fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style JupyterImages fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style IstioGateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style JupyterHub fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External services
    style Registry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Generated resources
    style StatefulSets fill:#50c8ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Services fill:#50c8ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style VirtualServices fill:#50c8ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
